<div class="mt-4">
  <div>
    <%= link_to "Modifier", listing_pricing_daily_price_path(listing_id: @listing, pricing_id: @listing.pricing), class: "btn btn-outline-primary float-sm-right" %>
    <h5 class="mt-5 mb-5">Prix par jour</h5>
    <p><span class="float-right label label-info label-pill"><%= @listing.pricing.base_price %> <%= @listing.pricing.currency %></span> Prix de base</p>
    <hr>
    <p class="form-text text-muted">Vous êtes responsable du choix du prix de votre vélo.</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <%= link_to "Modifier", listing_pricing_discounts_path(listing_id: @listing, pricing_id: @listing.pricing), class: "btn btn-outline-primary float-sm-right" %>
    <h5 class="mt-5 mb-5">Réductions en fonction de la durée de la location</h5>
    <p><span class="float-right label label-info label-pill"><%= @listing.pricing.average_weekly %> <%= @listing.pricing.currency %></span> Hebdomadaire moyen </p>
    <hr>
    <p><span class="float-right label label-info label-pill"><%= @listing.pricing.average_monthly %> <%= @listing.pricing.currency %></span> Mensuel moyen</p>
    <hr>
    <p class="form-text text-muted">Encouragez les cyclistes à louer votre vélo plus longtemps avec des réductions au mois ou à la semaine. <a href="#discountsModal" data-toggle="modal">En savoir plus</a></p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <%= link_to "Modifier", "#", class: "btn btn-outline-primary float-sm-right" %>
    <h5 class="mt-5 mb-5">Frais supplémentaires</h5>
    <p><span class="float-right label label-info label-pill"><%= @listing.pricing.maintenance_fee %> <%= @listing.pricing.currency %></span> Frais de maintenance</p>
    <hr>
    <p><span class="float-right label label-info label-pill"><%= @listing.pricing.security_deposit %> <%= @listing.pricing.currency %></span> Caution</p>
    <hr>
    <p><span class="float-right label label-info label-pill"><%= @listing.pricing.weekend_pricing %> <%= @listing.pricing.currency %></span> Tarif weekend</p>
    <hr>
  </div>
  <div>
    <%= link_to "Modifier", "#", class: "btn btn-outline-primary float-sm-right" %>
    <h5 class="mt-5 mb-5">Devise</h5>
    <span class="float-right label label-info label-pill"><%= @listing.pricing.currency %></span> Devise
    <hr>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render partial: "modals/discounts" %>
